definition: abbr. for Xinjiang 新疆[Xin1 jiang1] or Singapore 新加坡[Xin1 jia1 po1]/surname Xin

sentences.english: Maoxing block saliferous strata are mainly in 4 th Member, Funing Formation , Eocene Series.
sentences.chinese: 茅興塊段含鹽系地層主要爲始新統阜寧組四段。

sentences.english: The funnel-shaped self-potential curve of the Eocene sands is well marked.
sentences.chinese: 始新統砂層的漏斗形自然電位曲線形態很明顯。
